Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（ルフィ）『ワンピース』　１０周年！\N（一同）乾杯！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.53,0:00:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・『Ｓｈａｒｅ　Ｔｈｅ　Ｗｏｒｌｄ』\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.58,0:00:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.73,0:00:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.93,0:01:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.66,0:01:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:02:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
